@startuml worker_lifecycle
title Worker State Lifecycle

[*] --> Idle : addWorker()

Idle --> Working : assigned to workstation
Working --> Idle : released\n(cycle complete)
Working --> Blocked : notifyWorkerBusy()
Blocked --> Idle : notifyWorkerIdle()
Idle --> Idle : abandonWork()

Idle --> [*] : removeWorker()
Working --> [*] : removeWorker()
Blocked --> [*] : removeWorker()

note right of Idle
  Available for assignment
  to queued workstations
end note

note right of Working
  Executing steps at
  assigned workstation
end note

note right of Blocked
  Temporarily unavailable
  (fighting, sleeping, etc.)
  Released from workstation
end note

@enduml
